The issue is by default the  database is not connected. You have to connect it to your custom table to the database yourself. 
this tutorial shows you how :  https://youtu.be/7d2UMAIgOLQ?t=11107 

essentially your just going in the appsetttings.json in the ConnectionStrings you copying your Localdb name from SQL Sever Object  and adding your database name of your choosing should looks something like this :
"ConnectionStrings": {
    "DefaultConnection": "server=(localdb)\\ProjectModels;database=MyappChosenName;"
  }

